1811Ganthavippayutto dhammo ganthavippayuttassa dhammassa vipākapaccayena paccayo…  ekaṃ.
1812Ganthasampayutto dhammo ganthasampayuttassa dhammassa āhārapaccayena paccayo…  cattāri…  indriyapaccayena paccayo…  cattāri…  jhānapaccayena paccayo…  cattāri…  maggapaccayena paccayo…  cattāri…  sampayuttapaccayena paccayo…  cha.
